---
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-[1140px] mx-auto px-6">

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="section-tag">Como funciona</span>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.75rem,4vw,2.5rem);font-weight:600;margin-top:0.5rem;">5 passos para sua residência fiscal</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Steps: horizontal on desktop, vertical on mobile -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connector line desktop -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-6 left-0 right-0 h-px" style="background:#dfdede;z-index:0;margin: 0 80px;"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 relative z-10">
        {[
          { n:'01', icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>`, title:'Consulta gratuita', desc:'Entendemos seu perfil e desenhamos a estratégia ideal.' },
          { n:'02', icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>`, title:'Documentação', desc:'Preparamos e apostilamos todos os documentos necessários.' },
          { n:'03', icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"/>`, title:'1ª viagem a Assunção', desc:'~5 dias úteis para iniciar o processo de residência.' },
          { n:'04', icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8"/>`, title:'2ª viagem a Assunção', desc:'~5 dias úteis para retirar sua cédula paraguaia.' },
          { n:'05', icon: `<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>`, title:'Você é residente fiscal', desc:'Renda do exterior isenta. Estrutura funcionando.' },
        ].map((step) => (
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background:#8417aa;">
              <svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.75" set:html={step.icon}></svg>
            </div>
            <span style="font-family:'DM Sans';font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#07ffd2;background:#8417aa;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:99px;" class="mb-2">{step.n}</span>
            <h3 style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">{step.title}</h3>
            <p style="font-family:'DM Sans';font-size:0.82rem;color:#555;line-height:1.5;">{step.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-14">
      <a href="https://wa.me/5511913062315" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Começar meu processo</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
